    • Constructor Detail

      • ChatUser

        public ChatUser(ChatServer server,
                RakNetClientPeer peer,
                java.util.UUID uuid,
                java.lang.String username)
         throws java.lang.NullPointerException
        Creates a chat user.

        As soon as this user is created, a LOGIN_ACCEPTED packet will be sent to it. When a chat user is created, it is assumed that they are already validated.

        Parameters:
        server - the server that the user belongs to.
        peer - the peer.
        uuid - the universally unique ID.
        username - the username.
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the server, peer, uuid or username are null.
